=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_EnvGen_ex1 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_dark mixed sound, with complex characteristics, featuring punchy attack and impulsive envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, energy distribution is front_heavy, filtered with steep_rolloff character, and spectrally simple.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: very_dark
  crest_factor_db: impulsive
  envelope_flatness: very_dynamic
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: mixed
  spectral_complexity_mean: simple
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: front_heavy

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 0.0000
  harmonic_decay_rate: 0.0000
  harmonic_regularity: 0.0000
  pitch_clarity: 0.4401
  inharmonicity: 0.0000
  type: complex
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -0.9220
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: EnvGen Example 1
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Classes/EnvGen.html
// Tags: EnvGen, Classes, envelope
// ---
// --- Example 1 ---
{ PinkNoise.ar(EnvGen.kr(Env.perc, doneAction: Done.freeSelf)) }.play
